The ultimate driving machine.

00:00:06.906 --> 00:00:09.108
[upbeat rock music]

00:00:09.141 --> 00:00:14.847
♪ ♪

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:16.349
Hello and welcome
to Teaching Center.

00:00:16.382 --> 00:00:18.351
I'm Boyd Maxwell,
with today's top stories

00:00:18.384 --> 00:00:20.319
from the exciting world
of teaching.

00:00:20.352 --> 00:00:21.854
And I'm Perry Schmidt.

00:00:21.887 --> 00:00:23.222
Well, now we know.

00:00:23.255 --> 00:00:25.324
The long awaited announcement
by star English teacher

00:00:25.357 --> 00:00:29.496
Ruby Ruhf has sent teaching fans
across the nation into a frenzy.

00:00:30.763 --> 00:00:32.231
I've enjoyed my time
in Ohio very much,

00:00:32.264 --> 00:00:34.867
but I'm pleased to announce
that I'm taking my talents

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:38.471
back to New York City.
Thank you very much.

00:00:38.504 --> 00:00:42.108
Apparently, PS431 has made Ruby
an offer she couldn't refuse.

00:00:42.141 --> 00:00:43.810
$80 million guaranteed
over six years,

00:00:43.843 --> 00:00:46.546
with another $40 million
in incentives

00:00:46.579 --> 00:00:48.247
based on test scores.

00:00:48.280 --> 00:00:49.816
This salary puts her
right up there

00:00:49.849 --> 00:00:51.751
with Rockridge Elementary's
Katie Hope

00:00:51.784 --> 00:00:54.520
and William Wu
out of--

00:00:54.553 --> 00:00:56.489
Colgate Magnet!

00:00:57.923 --> 00:00:59.225
All right, let's take a look
at yesterday's

00:00:59.258 --> 00:01:01.928
high school teacher draft
from Radio City Music Hall,

00:01:01.961 --> 00:01:03.262
where Central Rapids High,

00:01:03.295 --> 00:01:06.099
recipient of the worst
test scores last semester,

00:01:06.132 --> 00:01:08.902
made the first pick
that was no surprise to anyone.

00:01:09.969 --> 00:01:12.004
[all cheering]

00:01:12.037 --> 00:01:15.408
For the first pick,
Central Rapids High takes...

00:01:15.441 --> 00:01:18.711
calculus teacher Mike Yoast
from Tulsa Teacher's College.

00:01:18.744 --> 00:01:20.246
[all cheering]

00:01:20.279 --> 00:01:22.915
(Key)
And just like that,
you're a millionaire. Ha ha.

00:01:22.948 --> 00:01:26.119
(Peele)
Mike Yoast
is an unbelievable story,

00:01:26.152 --> 00:01:28.020
his father living
from paycheck to paycheck

00:01:28.053 --> 00:01:29.455
as a humble
pro football player.

00:01:29.488 --> 00:01:31.124
Kid was a natural mathlete.

00:01:31.157 --> 00:01:32.391
You know he's gonna buy
his mom a house.

00:01:32.424 --> 00:01:33.559
- Oh, you know this.
- Oh, there's no way

00:01:33.592 --> 00:01:34.727
- around that.
- [laughs]

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:36.796
You owe your mom.
[laughs]

00:01:39.365 --> 00:01:40.933
(announcer)
Today's highlight of the day
is brought to you

00:01:40.966 --> 00:01:43.903
by the 100% Black Angus Beef
Thickburger

00:01:43.936 --> 00:01:46.806
on a fresh-baked bun
from Carl's Jr. and Hardee's.

00:01:48.507 --> 00:01:50.343
Now it's time
for the highlight of the day.

00:01:50.376 --> 00:01:52.879
[rock music]

00:01:52.912 --> 00:01:55.581
Star history teacher
Ashley Ferguson has been

00:01:55.614 --> 00:01:58.351
running up them test scores
over at Vinz Clortho High.

00:01:58.384 --> 00:02:00.019
- Okay.
- Whoo.

00:02:00.052 --> 00:02:02.522
Confederate forces
fired first.

00:02:02.555 --> 00:02:05.825
Can anyone tell me
where this battle took place?

00:02:05.858 --> 00:02:06.692
Now, look at this.

00:02:06.725 --> 00:02:09.328
She looks left,
then right,

00:02:09.361 --> 00:02:12.031
looks past the students
with their arms up in the air,

00:02:12.064 --> 00:02:13.332
- spots Max near the back...
(Key) Whoo.

00:02:13.365 --> 00:02:17.236
Sees that even though his hand
isn't up, he's engaged.

00:02:17.269 --> 00:02:17.937
Max?

00:02:17.970 --> 00:02:19.405
It was Fort Sumter?

00:02:19.438 --> 00:02:21.207
That's right.

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:22.942
Oh, come on.
See what she did there?

00:02:22.975 --> 00:02:24.510
She's bringing a introvert
into the discussion, y'all.

00:02:24.543 --> 00:02:27.280
That's a teacher of the year
play right there.

00:02:27.313 --> 00:02:29.115
That's right, Boyd.
You know, the confidence gained

00:02:29.148 --> 00:02:31.017
by Max by answering
that question correctly

00:02:31.050 --> 00:02:33.719
will enhance his performance
throughout the rest of the year.

00:02:33.752 --> 00:02:35.955
No doubt.
Coming up after the break,

00:02:35.988 --> 00:02:37.957
Mayfield Prep trades
French teacher Janeane Lowe

00:02:37.990 --> 00:02:40.059
to Skyline High
for a head librarian

00:02:40.092 --> 00:02:41.260
and two lunch ladies
to be named later.

00:02:41.293 --> 00:02:44.096
And we'll get the inside scoop
on the impending

00:02:44.129 --> 00:02:45.698
- teacher's strike that could...
- Uh-oh.

00:02:45.731 --> 00:02:46.832
Cripple the season.

00:02:46.865 --> 00:02:48.134
Next up,
on Teaching Center.

00:02:48.167 --> 00:02:49.902
Whoo.

